{
  "stem": "2226.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told you, good shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the march?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I mean, oh, on the march was lots of people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, in mine column-- in my-- it was columns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Two miles farther was a-- another march.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Two far-- two miles farther, another march.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was lots of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They liquidated all the camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In my column, was a few hundred.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not two-- a few hundred.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- absolute nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That is how we survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had-- we had, maybe, food for a week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we men-- we-- the men refused to eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We should cook the-- for the ladies a little bit hot water in that-- that way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So how we survived?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was, when we marched, there was-- [TEARFUL] there was lots-- lots of [INAUDIBLE] civilian-- Hollandish, Czechs, French.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So [INAUDIBLE], they all stand the road in the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how we were.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he want to risk his life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then [INAUDIBLE] he put me in [TEARFUL] a piece of bread, two apples, sometimes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And how long did you walk every day?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll tell you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We figured out [INAUDIBLE] we stopped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we made no more like 15, 20 kilometers a day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No more.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We couldn't go further.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- [INAUDIBLE] they were tired too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] we stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we couldn't go further.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, the Wermacht come-- the general from Wermacht come.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he starts to talk to-- to that commandant from the SS.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where is he taking us?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The war is over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He shouldn't take us farther.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The meantime, he took us, because commandant-- the general from the SS, he said, no, you can't leave them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You have to take them over to the next bush, and maybe we kill them.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
